window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Corporate lawyer Nicolo DeLuca is a made man. After the death of his beloved grandfather, he is sent by his cousin to live in Charlotte, NC, to head the mergers and acquisitions division of the DeLuca family business. As a condition of his new promotion, he must take a bride. Not any bride will do. He must take the hand of the daughter of the Baldwin family. This will prove to be his biggest merger yet.</p> <p>Plus-sized diva Simone Baldwin will do anything for family, including marry a man to keep the peace. After joining his law firm as a partner, she falls for the man she was promised to at the age of eight. When a rogue FBI agent targets Simone, she will need the family’s support to save her.</p> <p>Life, love, and loyalty are key in this BWWM mafia romance.</p>"; 
